Toledo Bar Association v. Banks.

[Cite as Toledo Bar Assn. v. Banks (1988), 37 Ohio St. 3d 601.]

No. D.D. 86-8 Submitted June 1, 1988 Decided June 29, 1988.

The application for reinstatement to the practice of law is granted. Gerald W. Banks is reinstated to the practice of law in the state of Ohio.

(For earlier case, see [1986], 28 Ohio St. 3d 125, 28 OBR 223, 502 N.E. 2d 1021.)

Moyer, C.J., Sweeney, Locher, Holmes, Douglas, Wright and H. Brown, JJ., concur.
